MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

92-1460. In re Election of June 2, 1992 for the Office of Representative to the United States House of Representatives from the Sixth District of Ohio. Holmes, J.

This cause originated in this court on the filing of an election contest petition under R.C. 3515.09. Upon consideration of contestor’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application to dismiss be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective August 25, 1992.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and the same is hereby, dismissed.
